OL,7,FStephen Finney - "The inquiry process
OL,8,Fmeans we're no longer treated like
OL,9,Fconspiracy theorists."
OL,11,F"I refuse to be defined by
OL,12,Fhaemophilia, or by infected blood,"
OL,13,Fsays Stephen Finney, at his home in
OL,14,FDorset, "but I can't pretend my life
OL,15,Fwouldn't have been completely
OL,16,Fdifferent if it hadn't happened".
OL,18,FStephen, now 53, has never married or
OL,19,Fhad children, something he's deeply
OL,20,Fsad about.
