OL,3,C'We were cheaper than chimps' -
OL,4,CCampaigners call for justice over
OL,5,Cinfected blood
OL,7,F"It just wasn't an option for me," he
OL,8,Fsays. "I was a two years old when I
OL,9,Fwas infected with Hepatitis B, quite
OL,10,Fpossibly from my very first use of
OL,11,FFactor VIII."
OL,13,FHe later passed the infection on to
OL,14,Fhis mother, who herself needed
OL,15,Fextensive treatment. He doesn't know
OL,16,Fif the infection contributed to her
OL,17,Fill health and premature death.
OL,19,FThen, in 1985, a bombshell.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/15
