OL,7,F"At 14 I found out I'd been infected
OL,8,Fwith HIV and was told I could be dead
OL,9,Fwithin months," he says.
OL,11,F"It was terrifying. Since then,
OL,12,Fpsychologically, I've been walking
OL,13,Famongst the tombstones every day."
