OL,3,C'We were cheaper than chimps' -
OL,4,CCampaigners call for justice over
OL,5,Cinfected blood
OL,7,FHe may have defied the odds, but his
OL,8,Flife has been blighted by ill-health
OL,9,Fand dominated by campaigning for
OL,10,Fjustice and accountability, not just
OL,11,Ffor himself, but for the thousands
OL,12,Fdirectly impacted by what's been
OL,13,Fdescribed as the worst treatment
OL,14,Fdisaster in the history of the NHS.
OL,16,FNext month, on 20 May, a public
OL,17,Finquiry, led by Sir Brian Langstaff,
OL,18,Fwill report back following a five-year
OL,19,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/15
