OL,5,Cinfected blood
OL,7,FIt's been designed to address why the
OL,8,Fscandal happened, who knew what and
OL,9,Fwhen, whether further deaths could
OL,10,Fhave been prevented, and how best to
OL,11,Fcompensate people, not just for the
OL,12,Finfection, but the trauma that went
OL,13,Fwith it.
OL,15,FAmong the questions being asked are
OL,16,Fwhether children were used as guinea
OL,17,Fpigs to test the infectivity of blood
OL,18,Fproducts, something Stephen is in no
OL,19,Fdoubt about.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/15
