OL,3,C'We were cheaper than chimps' -
OL,4,CCampaigners call for justice over
OL,5,Cinfected blood
OL,7,F"They were doing the tests on us,
OL,8,Fbecause chimpanzees were expensive,"
OL,9,Fhe says.
OL,11,F"There's documentation that actually
OL,12,Fsaid that in the inquiry - chimps are
OL,13,Ftoo expensive to be tested on, so do
OL,14,Fit on the patients. And we were the
OL,15,Fperfect control group, a godsend for
OL,16,Fthem."
OL,18,FHe's also angry at the length of time
OL,19,Fit's taken to hold the inquiry.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/15
