OL,3,C'We were cheaper than chimps' -
OL,4,CCampaigners call for justice over
OL,5,Cinfected blood
OL,7,F"All of this should really have been
OL,8,Fdone 20 or 30 years ago," he says.
OL,10,F"Sadly, so much time has elapsed for
OL,11,Fall of those people that could've and
OL,12,Fperhaps should've done jail time are
OL,13,Flong since gone."
OL,15,FDoes the cynic in him believe that was
OL,16,Fintentional?
OL,18,F"Absolutely. For 30 years I've been
OL,19,Fcampaigning and their attitude has
OL,20,Fbeen, well they're going to die
OL,21,Fanyway."
