OL,7,FIt's a view shared by many
OL,8,Fcampaigners, who point out that
OL,9,Fvictims are continuing to die at a
OL,10,Frate of one every three days.
OL,12,FA haemophiliac, Stephen grew up in
OL,13,FBuckinghamshire and was treated at the
OL,14,FOxford Haemotology Centre, one of the
OL,15,Flargest and most progressive centres
OL,16,Fin the country.
