OL,7,FMore than a third died, including
OL,9,FBut it wasn't only haemophiliacs -
OL,10,Fthousands more were infected during
OL,11,Froutine transfusions after childbirth
OL,12,For surgery.
OL,14,FCoinciding with AIDS in the 1980s,
OL,15,Fmany victims had to endure horrific
OL,16,Fabuse.
OL,18,F"The stigma that existed at the time
OL,19,Fwas crippling and terrifying," says
OL,20,FClive Smith, Chair of the Haemophilia
OL,21,FSociety."
