OL,3,C'We were cheaper than chimps' -
OL,4,CCampaigners call for justice over
OL,5,Cinfected blood
OL,7,F"People lost jobs, children were
OL,8,Fbanned from schools, some had abusive
OL,9,Fgraffiti painted on their homes.
OL,11,F"There was a climate of fear, to such
OL,12,Fan extent that even now, many people
OL,13,Fgiving evidence at the inquiry have
OL,14,Fdone so anonymously."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/15
