OL,7,FThe Government has already accepted
OL,8,Fthe moral case for compensation - some
OL,9,Fvictims and spouses have received
OL,10,Finterim payments, but a final
OL,11,Fcompensation scheme including parents
OL,12,Fand children, has yet to be set up,
OL,13,Fthe total cost likely to run into
OL,14,Fbillions.
