OL,3,C'We were cheaper than chimps' -
OL,4,CCampaigners call for justice over
OL,5,Cinfected blood
OL,7,FStephen says nothing can bring back
OL,8,Fhis lost years, but he hopes the
OL,9,Finquiry will help ensure nothing like
OL,10,Fthis can ever happen again, and look
OL,11,Fat the role of pharmaceutical
OL,12,Fcompanies, civil servants, ministers
OL,13,Fand senior doctors in the NHS.
OL,15,FAnd the inquiry process in itself, has
OL,16,Fit been useful?
OL,18,F"Yes, hugely" he says. "I've told Sir
OL,19,FBrian that it's been the best therapy
OL,20,Fthat money can't buy, because it's
OL,21,Fvindication.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/15
