OL,3,C'We were cheaper than chimps' -
OL,4,CCampaigners call for justice over
OL,5,Cinfected blood
OL,7,F"The inquiry process has basically
OL,8,Fmeant that we're no longer considered
OL,9,Fas nutters anymore for sounding off
OL,10,Fabout some sort of wild conspiracy
OL,11,Ftheory.
OL,13,F"You know, this actually happened and
OL,14,Fit was avoidable.
OL,16,F"There were many points along the way
OL,17,Fat which individuals and organisations
OL,18,Fcould and should have intervened but
OL,19,Fdidn't."
